com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.tone_analyzer.v3.model

Class UtteranceAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.service.model.GenericModel
      • com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.tone_analyzer.v3.model.UtteranceAnalysis

  • public class UtteranceAnalysis
extends GenericModel
    This object represents the results of Tone Chat analysis on an utterance. It has the utterance text from the original input. It holds a list of scores for individual chat tones.
